Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.75,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,信じられない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. Who would've thought she could recover from that condition.
