Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thermal insulation package, is it food?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.39,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
