Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.35,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,凍ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's frozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoma, you're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.97,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,晶馬　時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
