Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Himari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.26,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ　ひまりの事を頼んだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.13,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a restless guy.
