Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:01.58,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　ぼくはただの好運だと思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, I thought we were just lucky.
