Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.64,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら～　お前え冷たいな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold to me!
