Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's looking at {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.34,默认日文对话-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺のこと見てる　なんでせつない
